We go there every week to play cricket. That's very big ground and have multiple section where you can play different games, learn drones and have some family time.

This ground is awesome. Can play cricket, baseball and football too. Mostly weekends this place is fully packed.
A place for some Me-time, the sound of rooster crowing is surprisingly soothing. A reminder that tomorrow will be better~明天会更好！
Look our for Parrots Fan Club at 9 am on Sunday where they execise their birds. Spectacular sight where the Parakeets fly in formation...
Wonderful success of a city park. Lots of wildlife too if you take a deep breath and soak it all in.
